July 11 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Cogeco Cable Inc and Fortuna Silver Mines, on Friday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Cogeco Cable Inc <CCA.TO>: Barclays, National Bank Financial raise target price on co * Grenville Strategic Royalty <GRC.V>: National Bank Financial resumes with outperform   Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Friday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Cogeco Cable Inc <CCA.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target price to C$70 from C$67 * Cogeco Cable Inc <CCA.TO>: Barclays raises target to C$67 from C$65; rating overweight * Fortuna Silver Mines <FVI.TO>: CIBC raises target to C$6.50 from C$5; sector performer * Grenville Strategic Royalty <GRC.V>: National Bank Financial resumes with outperform * Grenville Strategic Royalty <GRC.V>: National Bank Financial resumes with target C$1.15 * Inter Pipeline <IPL.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target price to C$34 from C$33